item.title: CVE-2022-4063|2024-08-03T01:27:54.195Z -- unknown -- inpost%20gallery
item.description: The InPost Gallery WordPress plugin before 2.1.4.1 insecurely uses PHP's extract() function when rendering HTML views, allowing attackers to force the inclusion of malicious files & URLs, which may enable them to run code on servers.
